                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>The <addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dr Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I have to acknowledge<lb/> yours of <date>29th</date> ultimo and to\n                thank<lb/> you for acceding to my request<lb/> respecting my little work,<lb/> which\n                will <add>?</add> be published<lb/> here on <date>1st July</date>, and I will<lb/>\n                endeavor to sent you 1 doz<lb/> copies as near that<add>?</add> time as<lb/>\n                possible. I concluded from<lb/> your note <add>?</add> it that<lb/> you are\n                agreeable to the<lb/> terms I proposed, 25 pc commission.<lb/> I think my book must\n                be<lb/> rebound cheap even in the<lb/> American sense of the word,<lb/> as each part\n                will comprise</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37m04s0b/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
