                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>about 180 pages of matter, with the<lb/> best paper and type for 2/<add>?</add><lb/>\n                a part. It<add>?</add> will I hope be concluded in <date>October</date><lb/> I have\n                a first rate list of<lb/> subscribers all the heads of<lb/> the nation <persName>Dr\n                    Adler</persName>\n                <persName>Sir Moses<lb/> Montefiore</persName><add>?</add> the\n                    <persName>Rothschild's</persName><lb/>\n                <add>?</add> and <persName>Dr Berusch</persName><lb/> has introduced it very\n                favorably<lb/> to public notice in the Hebrew<lb/> Observer. I shall be obliged<lb/>\n                by your putting in the follow<lb/>ing <sic>advertizement</sic> in the<lb/> Occident\n                for <date>July</date>, and I should<lb/> wish it continued till\n                <date>October</date><lb/> when you will please alter<lb/> it to announce the\n                second<lb/> part; though I will write<lb/> previously in case any thing<lb/> should\n                prevent its publication<lb/> at that time.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37m04s0b/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
