                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>“To be published in two parts<lb/> price 2/. each part.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Now ready Post<add>?</add>\n                <add>?</add><lb/>\n                <date>Sabbath</date> Evenings at Home<lb/> or<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> Conversations on the<lb/> Jewish Religion its Spirit<lb/> and\n                Observances by</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Mi<add>?</add> Mendes Belesario</persName><lb/> Published\n                in <placeName>London</placeName> by <persName>Mes Joel</persName><lb/>\n                <placeName>42 South Cripplegate</placeName>. To be had<lb/> in <placeName>New\n                    York</placeName> of <persName>Mr Daniel Wolff</persName><lb/>\n                <placeName>32 South St.</placeName>\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                <persName>Revd<lb/> Isaac Leeser</persName> &amp;</p>\n            <p>You will please put this in<lb/> proper order for me.<lb/> and now having\n                concluded<lb/> my business arrangements,<lb/> permit me Dr Sir to express my<lb/>\n                sincere regret for the severe<add>?</add><lb/> loss you have sustained by<lb/> the\n                fire, for which I trust<lb/> you may meet with compen<lb/>sation by an increased\n                sale<lb/> of your books, in which business <add>?</add></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p37m04s0b/canvas/p3"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
