                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>it will not be in my power to<lb/> assist you, at least as regards the<lb/> Prayer\n                Books; for of course our<lb/>\n                <add>?</add> consisted<add>?</add>\n                <persName>Mr De Sola's</persName><lb/> are in general circulation among<lb/> our\n                congregation. I understand<lb/> you contemplate reprinting his<lb/> in\n                    <placeName>America</placeName>, and that your<lb/> dependence lies there, for\n                I<lb/> think it right to <add>?</add> that<lb/> you are not likely to meet<lb/> with\n                much support here. You<lb/> have <add>?</add> been misinformed<lb/> as to\n                    <persName>Mr Genese's</persName> influence<lb/> he could do nothing\n                whatever<lb/> I regret much to find that<lb/> you have still so many powerful<lb/>\n                things to contend with, but<lb/> think you are mistaken in<lb/> your impression of\n                    <persName>Mr Morais</persName><lb/> unless he be greatly altered, for<lb/> I\n                knew him intimately, very<lb/> deep knowledge of Hebrew is<lb/> derived from him,\n                and I</p>"
                  },
